                                                  melodic variations for the Hallelujah (same as
                                                  https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1110Anqasa)</title>
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>

                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
                    <locus from="100v" to="102r" facs="105">Fols 100v–102r</locus>
                    <title>Instructions for variations in the recitations of the melody, Araray, <foreign xml:lang="gez">አራራይ፡</foreign></title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ግዕዝ፡ የሚከተላቼው፡ አራራዮች፡ ሰገደ፡ ጢስ፡ በጎልጎታ፡ ዘይገለብቦ፡ ለሰማይ፡ በደመና፡ ወያስተዴሉ፡ አነኒ፡ አንትሙ፡ አኃውየ፡ ወይእዜኒ፡ ወልደ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ፀወንነ፡ ሐዋርያቲሁ፡ ከበበ፡
                      ወልድ፡ ናሁ፡ ይሠርቅ፡ ኮከብ፡ ኢይደግም፡ እንከ፡ አጥመቆሙ፡</incipit>
                  </msItem>
                </msItem>

